#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3324
#, no-c-format
msgid "child(childname)"
msgstr "बाल(बालनाम)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns an instance of \"RObject\" representing the child "
"<emphasis>childname</emphasis> of this object."
msgstr ""
"अस्य वस्तुनः बालकं <emphasis>childname</emphasis> प्रतिनिधियति \"RObject\" इत्यस्य "
"उदाहरणं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Class \"RObjectArray\""
msgstr "वर्ग \"RObjectArray\" ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An array of RObject instances. An instance of this class can be obtained by "
"using <command>makeRObjectArray(objectnames)</command>. It is particularly "
"useful when dealing with varslots which allow to select multiple objects."
msgstr ""
"RObject उदाहरणानां एकः सरणी । अस्य वर्गस्य एकं उदाहरणं "
"<command>makeRObjectArray(objectnames)</command> इत्यस्य उपयोगेन प्राप्तुं शक्यते । "
"विशेषतया varslots इत्यनेन सह व्यवहारे उपयोगी भवति यत् बहुविधवस्तूनि चयनं कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3330
#, no-c-format
msgid "include()-function"
msgstr "समावेश()-कार्य"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>include(filename)</command> can be used to include a separate JS "
"file."
msgstr ""
"<command>include(filename)</command> इत्यस्य उपयोगेन पृथक् JS सञ्चिकां समावेशयितुं "
"शक्यते ।"

